Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:26.07,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}mebaeru hana no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:32.33,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}omoi no kakera afurete kuru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.33,0:22:45.01,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}kono te ni moraeta kimi no nukumori
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.01,0:22:54.01,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}takaramono ni naru mirai he michibiite kureta ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:23:03.94,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}zutto kimi no koe wo oikaketeita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.94,0:23:09.45,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}itsu kara nan darou tsuyoku natta ne
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:16.54,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}kiiroi sekai sagashita mono wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:24.25,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}tabiji no hate ni kitto mitsukaru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:13.35,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}Po mrazivé vichřici,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.18,0:22:19.48,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}v níž suchý vítr vál,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:26.07,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}se ve mně začínají vytvářet různé pocity,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:32.33,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}jako v květině, která brzy vykvete.
